parameters: \nc<Saki>I'm back from the outside work. Haa, I'm exhausted...

You're back?

\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>Wait, please, Senpai! Isn't that customer one of my
regulars?

\nc<Senpai>But Saki, you were out on the outside work. Besides, right
now I'm much better suited for him, don't you think?

\nc<Timid Customer>I will definitely save up money to fully enjoy the main

from.
\nc<Senpai>By the way, did you buy the lemon water?
\bustMsgExp[1, 0]\nc<Saki>Ah, yes. I've got a whole box of it right here...

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>Lemon water after a blowjob is truly exceptional, isn't
